    && apt-get -qq -y autoremove \

    && groupadd -g 1000 -r app \

    TZ="UTC"

COPY requirements.txt /tmp/
RUN pip install --no-cache-dir -q -r /tmp/requirements.txt
RUN mkdir -p /app
WORKDIR /app
COPY . /app
RUN pip install --no-cache-dir -q -e /app

USER app:app
CMD ["yente", "serve"]
